flowchart TD
    A["USB Webcam"] --> B["webcam_capture.py"]
    B -->|writes| C["/tmp/camera_frame.jpg"]
    C --> D["lane_follow.py\n(runs sidewalk adapter)"]
    D -->|always writes| E["/tmp/model_output.json"]

    D -->|"Lane Follow mode:\nwrites joystick directly"| G["/tmp/joystick"]

    E -->|"Exp Auto mode"| F["exp_auto.py\n(pure pursuit steering + throttle)"]
    F -->|writes| G

    G --> H["output_serial.py"]
    H -->|serial| I["Arduino"]
    I --> J["Motors"]

    WEB["Web UI :5000"] -->|"manual joystick"| G

    style A fill:#1a3a5c,color:#fff,stroke:#0d1f33
    style B fill:#2c2c2c,color:#fff,stroke:#1a1a1a
